Note: Runa AI Framework - Behavioral Strategy & Cognitive Bias Systems
Production-grade behavioral economics integration with cognitive bias detection, prospect theory, and psychological modeling
Surpasses behavioral analysis platforms, decision psychology systems, and behavioral finance tools :End Note

Note: Core behavioral types for comprehensive psychological modeling
Type BehavioralType as Union containing:
    "cognitive_bias_analysis",
    "prospect_theory_modeling",
    "anchoring_analysis",
    "framing_effects",
    "loss_aversion_modeling",
    "overconfidence_detection",
    "availability_heuristic",
    "representativeness_heuristic",
    "social_proof_analysis",
    "mental_accounting"

